---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Getting Started" description="Install EDDI, create your first agent, and start chatting in 5 minutes." fullWidth={true}>

<section class="gs-hero hero-gradient-bg">
	<div class="gs-hero-inner">
		<h1>Get Started with EDDI</h1>
		<p class="gs-subtitle">Install EDDI, create your first agent, and start chatting in 5 minutes.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<article class="gs-content">

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>Prerequisites</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Docker</strong> (recommended) or Java 25+</li>
			<li>An LLM provider API key (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini, or a local Ollama instance)</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>1. Start EDDI with Docker</h2>
		<p>The fastest way to run EDDI:</p>
		<pre><code>docker run -p 7070:7070 labsai/eddi:latest</code></pre>
		<p>EDDI will be available at <code>http://localhost:7070</code>.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>2. Connect via MCP</h2>
		<p>If you use <strong>Claude Desktop</strong> or any MCP-compatible client, add EDDI as an MCP server:</p>
		<pre><code>{`{
  "mcpServers": {
    "eddi": {
      "url": "http://localhost:7070/mcp"
    }
  }
}`}</code></pre>
		<p>Now you can interact with EDDI's 39 MCP tools directly from your AI assistant.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>3. Create Your First Agent</h2>
		<p>Use the <code>setup_agent</code> MCP tool to create a fully working agent in one call:</p>
		<pre><code>{`setup_agent(
  name: "My first agent",
  systemPrompt: "You are a helpful assistant that answers questions clearly.",
  provider: "anthropic",
  modelId: "claude-sonnet-4-6"
)`}</code></pre>
		<p>This creates the rules, LLM config, workflow, agent, and deploys it — all in one step.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>4. Chat with Your Agent</h2>
		<pre><code>{`chat_with_agent(agentId: "<your-agent-id>", message: "Hello! What can you do?")`}</code></pre>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-section">
		<h2>5. Open the Manager UI</h2>
		<p>Navigate to <code>http://localhost:7070</code> to visually manage your agents, workflows, and conversations with the EDDI Manager.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="gs-next-steps">
		<h2>What's Next?</h2>
		<div class="gs-cards">
			<a href="/features/overview/" class="gs-card">
				<strong>All Features</strong>
				<span>Explore everything EDDI offers</span>
			</a>
			<a href="/features/mcp-server/" class="gs-card">
				<strong>MCP Server</strong>
				<span>Browse all 39 MCP tools</span>
			</a>
			<a href="https://docs.labs.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="gs-card">
				<strong>Documentation ↗</strong>
				<span>Deep-dive into architecture & APIs</span>
			</a>
			<a href="/enterprise/why-eddi/" class="gs-card">
				<strong>Why EDDI?</strong>
				<span>The enterprise case for EDDI</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</article>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.gs-hero {
		padding: calc(var(--nav-height, 4rem) + 4rem) 1.5rem 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.gs-hero-inner {
		max-width: 42rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.gs-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.gs-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.gs-content {
		max-width: 48rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 1.5rem 6rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
	}

	.gs-content h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.gs-content p {
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.gs-content ul {
		padding-left: 1.25rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.gs-content pre {
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
		overflow-x: auto;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	html[data-theme='dark'] .gs-content pre {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}
	html[data-theme='light'] .gs-content pre {
		background: #f5f6f8;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.gs-section {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		padding-bottom: 3rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.gs-next-steps {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.gs-cards {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.gs-card {
		display: block;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	html[data-theme='dark'] .gs-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}
	html[data-theme='light'] .gs-card {
		background: #f5f6f8;
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.gs-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.gs-card strong {
		display: block;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.gs-card span {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-subtle);
	}

	@media (max-width: 40rem) {
		.gs-cards {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
